<TEXT PARTNO="005">
<COREF ID="14" TYPE="IDENT">Ko Yu - fen</COREF> states that it is not difficult to understand these trends against the backdrop of society at that time .
<COREF ID="3" TYPE="IDENT">Taiwan Outlaws of the Marsh</COREF> was broadcast just after the first direct popular elections for municipal mayors and provincial governor , when <COREF ID="43" TYPE="IDENT">the " underground " call - in television programs</COREF> were at <COREF ID="43" TYPE="IDENT">their</COREF> peak of popularity , and when discussion of " Taiwanese identity " was at a fever pitch .
