<TEXT PARTNO="006">
The hard - pressed daughter in law
The story of The Astonishing Daughter - in - Law is quite simple .
<COREF ID="66" TYPE="IDENT">The daughter - in - law , played by <COREF ID="3" TYPE="IDENT">Chang Yu - yen</COREF> ,</COREF> is mistreated by <COREF ID="81" TYPE="IDENT"><COREF ID="66" TYPE="IDENT">her</COREF> mother - in - law</COREF> , and , with outsiders butting in and causing trouble , <COREF ID="66" TYPE="IDENT">she</COREF> gets abused from beginning to end .
