<COREF ID="9" TYPE="IDENT">Television stations</COREF> have always based <COREF ID="9" TYPE="IDENT">their</COREF> decisions on ratings , and it is virtually impossible to expect that <COREF ID="9" TYPE="IDENT">they</COREF> will change a proven formula .
