Because <COREF ID="19" TYPE="IDENT">the series</COREF> was so popular , <COREF ID="41" TYPE="IDENT">FTV</COREF> seized the opportunity and presented a sequel based on the loves and hates of the third generation , which , as expected , also was very well received .
<COREF ID="19" TYPE="IDENT">Springtime Stepmother 's Heart</COREF> pulled <COREF ID="41" TYPE="IDENT">FTV</COREF> financially out of the red and into the black , and is considered an extremely remarkable event in <COREF ID="63" TYPE="IDENT">Taiwan</COREF> television history .
