<COREF ID="71" TYPE="IDENT">A show</COREF> can not be popular simply by using <COREF ID="6" TYPE="IDENT">Taiwanese language</COREF> , <COREF ID="15" TYPE="IDENT">she</COREF> says - the audience must be able to identify with <COREF ID="71" TYPE="IDENT">it</COREF> .
