<TEXT PARTNO="008">
<COREF ID="14" TYPE="IDENT">ON programming</COREF>
The success of <COREF ID="30" TYPE="IDENT">serials</COREF> means that TV stations in <COREF ID="66" TYPE="IDENT">Taiwan</COREF> just keep on cranking <COREF ID="30" TYPE="IDENT">them</COREF> out , broadcasting <COREF ID="10" TYPE="IDENT">episodes</COREF> as quickly as <COREF ID="10" TYPE="IDENT">they</COREF> are shot .
