Talent flow
As interactions between <COREF ID="33" TYPE="IDENT">Taiwan</COREF> and <COREF ID="64" TYPE="IDENT">the PRC</COREF> have grown , over the past few years there have been many cases of cooperative filming involving <COREF ID="33" TYPE="IDENT">Taiwan</COREF> , <COREF ID="21" TYPE="IDENT">Hong Kong</COREF> and <COREF ID="64" TYPE="IDENT">mainland China</COREF> , or of the hiring of technicians or performers from one area to work in another .
